name: PatxiOS
body:
### Welcome to PatxiOS.
PatxiOS is an open source Arduino Based operating system made by a 13 years old maker 

### Materials to build PatxiGlass
1. -Arduino pro mini x1
1. -Oled screen 0.96 x1
1. -Bluetooth module HC-05 x1
1. -Wires x10
1. -Mirror x1 
1. -Acrillic plate x1
1. -battery x1
   




   Code is life.
